nguShama waseHarodi; nguElika waseHarodi;
nguHeletse wasePeleti; nguIra unyana kaIkeshe waseTekowa:
nguAbhiyezere waseAnatoti; nguMebhunayi umHusha;
nguTsalimon umAhowa; nguMaharayi waseNetofa;
nguHelebhe, unyana kaBhahana waseNetofa; nguItayi, unyana kaRibhayi, waseGibheha yoonyana bakaBhenjamin;
nguBhenaya wasePiraton; nguHidayi wasezihlanjeni zaseGahashe;
nguAbhihalebhon waseArabha; nguAzemavete waseBhahurim;
nguEliyabha waseShahalebhon; nguBhene-yashen; nguYonatan;
