wathabathela eYordan empumalanga, lonke ilizwe laseGiliyadi, elamaGadi, nelamaRubhen, nelamaManase;  wathabathela eArohere, engasemlanjaneni oyiArnon, elaseGiliyadi nelaseBhashan.
