Ke wena, wakuzila, yithambise intloko yakho, ubuhlambe ubuso bakho,
ukuze ungabonakali ebantwini ukuba uzilile, ubonakale kuYihlo osemfihlekweni; aze uYihlo obona emfihlekweni akubuyisele ekuhleni.
