Nguwuphi na ke kuni onokuthi ngokuxhala ongeze ebukhulwini bakhe ikubhite ibe nye?
Kanjalo yini na ukuba nixhalele into yokwambatha? Gqalani iinyibiba zasendle, ukuhluma kwazo; azibulaleki, azisonti nokusonta;
ke ndithi kuni, noSolomon kubo bonke ubunewunewu bakhe,  wayengavathiswanga nanjenganye kuzo ezi.
