Yabonani, ndinixelele ngenxa engaphambili.
Ukuba ngoko bathi kuni, Nanko entlango, musani ukuphuma niye. Nokuba bathi, Nanko emagumbini, musani ukukholwa.
Kuba kwanjengokuba umbane uthi uphume empumalanga,  ubonakale kude kuse entshonalanga, kuya kuba njalo nokufika koNyana woMntu.
