Yoshuwa unyana kaNun wesusa amadoda amabini aziintlola,  esithi ngasese, Hambani niye kulikhangela ilizwe neYeriko.  Ahamba ke, aya endlwini yenkazana elihenyukazi, egama linguRahabhi, alala khona.
